snippet.title: Installing JDK 1.8 and 9 on Windows for Java Beginners
snippet.description:
Learn how to install and set up JDK 1.8 and 9 side by side by installing both and modifying your PATH environment variables. We'll also run one of the official examples, and compile our own Hello World program from the terminal. A brief word at the end is mentioned about IDE choice.

Text version and source code available at:
https://www.devdungeon.com/content/installing-jdk-18-and-9-windows-java-development
